measurements.description:
Approximately 240 flowers and six buds on 24 7.9-cm inflorescences;
	 arising from leaf axils on four fanlike growths on a 7-cm x 5-cm cork mount,
	 leaves 0.6cm wide, 5.5cm long, fine white roots with white hairs, root tips green;
	 flowers translucent white;
	 sepals and petals lanceolate;
	 spadelike lip translucent white; anther cap bright green;
	 pollinia yellow; substance translucent; texture crystalline;
	 light, grass like fragrance.
